<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 13:24:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在超光流体中游泳的微小物体逆流运动</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tiny-objects-swimming-in-a-superfluid-of-light-move-against-the-flow</link><description>超流体是一种有趣的物质状态，其中粒子的行为就像一个巨大的集体波，使它们能够在没有任何摩擦的情况下流动。当这种流体以低于特定阈值的速度流过固定障碍物时，它会绕着障碍物移动，而不会减慢速度或施加任何阻力。然而，超过这个临界速度，超流体状态开始崩溃，来自流动的能量以流体中的波纹和涡流的形式消散。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tiny-objects-swimming-in-a-superfluid-of-light-move-against-the-flow2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 13:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tiny-objects-swimming-in-a-superfluid-of-light-move-against-the-flow</guid></item><item><title>在单量子系统中观察到的局域化物理的五个阶段</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/five-phases-of-localization-physics-observed-in-a-single-quantum-system</link><description>中国的物理学家在单个量子系统内观察到局域化物理的五个阶段。由深圳南方科技大学王玉成和范景云领导的团队利用先进的光子平台，证明了局域物理学可能比物理学家预期的要丰富得多。他们的结果发表在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/five-phases-of-localization-physics-observed-in-a-single-quantum-system.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 13:09:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/five-phases-of-localization-physics-observed-in-a-single-quantum-system</guid></item><item><title>没有大脑的海泡如何在没有神经或肌肉的情况下仍然“感觉”到触摸并在几秒钟内爬走</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-a-brainless-sea-blob-still-feels-touch-and-crawls-away-in-seconds-without-nerves-or-muscles</link><description>对于直径只有几毫米的扁平海洋生物来说，轻轻一戳就会立即被认为是危险。 Trichoplax adhaerens 是一种没有头部、大脑或肌肉的半透明斑点，一旦被触摸，几秒钟内就会跑开。想象一下扁平的多细胞变形虫作为一个整体移动：Trichoplax 仅约 20 微米厚，几毫米宽。它通过敲击下上皮（底面）上的数万根纤毛在表面上滑行，就像在水面上拖动的微观桨一样。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-a-brainless-sea-blob-still-feels-touch-and-crawls-away-in-seconds-without-nerves-or-muscles2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 12:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-a-brainless-sea-blob-still-feels-touch-and-crawls-away-in-seconds-without-nerves-or-muscles</guid></item><item><title>15 原子铱纳米团簇可保持 20 小时稳定，性能优于商业催化剂</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/15-atom-iridium-nanoclusters-stay-stable-20-hours-outperform-commercial-catalysts</link><description>来自东北大学、东京理科大学、范德比尔特大学和阿德莱德大学的一个国际研究小组发现了一种新颖且极其简单的方法，可以在环境空气中精确合成极小的铱纳米团簇。此前，这样的壮举被认为极具挑战性。此外，纳米团簇的质量活性比传统市售铱催化剂高出 1.5 倍，同时保持持续运行稳定性超过 20 小时而不降解。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/15-atom-iridium-nanoclusters-stay-stable-20-hours-outperform-commercial-catalysts2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 12:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/15-atom-iridium-nanoclusters-stay-stable-20-hours-outperform-commercial-catalysts</guid></item><item><title>通过扭转六方氮化硼原子薄层来控制微小量子光源的新方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-new-way-to-control-tiny-quantum-light-sources-by-twisting-atomically-thin-layers-of-hexagonal-boron-nitride</link><description>在一篇论文中&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-new-way-to-control-tiny-quantum-light-sources-by-twisting-atomically-thin-layers-of-hexagonal-boron-nitride.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 12:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/a-new-way-to-control-tiny-quantum-light-sources-by-twisting-atomically-thin-layers-of-hexagonal-boron-nitride</guid></item><item><title>科学家刚刚发现眼睛违背了长期以来的视觉规则</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-just-discovered-the-eye-defies-a-long-held-rule-of-vision</link><description>耶鲁大学领导的一项研究发现，视网膜视觉通路之间存在意想不到的沟通，而这些通路被认为是单独运作的。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-just-discovered-the-eye-defies-a-long-held-rule-of-vision.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 12:09:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-just-discovered-the-eye-defies-a-long-held-rule-of-vision</guid></item><item><title>机器人交通拥堵的惊人解决方案</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-surprising-fix-for-robot-traffic-jams</link><description>哈佛大学的研究人员发现，为机器人运动添加一点随机性可以防止拥堵并显着提高拥挤群体中的效率。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-surprising-fix-for-robot-traffic-jams2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-surprising-fix-for-robot-traffic-jams</guid></item><item><title>超越 DNA：科学家发现打破遗传学规则的遗传</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/beyond-dna-scientists-discover-inheritance-that-breaks-the-rules-of-genetics</link><description>科学家发现，一些遗传特征可以绕过传统的遗传学规则，揭示了超越 DNA 的令人惊讶的新遗传层。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/beyond-dna-scientists-discover-inheritance-that-breaks-the-rules-of-genetics.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/beyond-dna-scientists-discover-inheritance-that-breaks-the-rules-of-genetics</guid></item><item><title>不可修补的“usbliter8”漏洞破坏了 Apple A12 和 A13 SecureROM 启动链</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/unpatchable-usbliter8-exploit-breaks-apple-a12-and-a13-securerom-boot-chain</link><description>Paradigm Shift 的安全研究人员发布了一个有效的漏洞，称为&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/unpatchable-usbliter8-exploit-breaks-apple-a12-and-a13-securerom-boot-chain2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/unpatchable-usbliter8-exploit-breaks-apple-a12-and-a13-securerom-boot-chain</guid></item><item><title>Gentlemen RaaS 使用 GentleKiller EDR 框架针对 400 个安全进程</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-gentlemen-raas-uses-gentlekiller-edr-framework-targeting-400-security-processes</link><description>ESET 表示，Gentlemen RaaS 为附属公司提供了 GentleKiller EDR-killer 套件，针对 48 个安全工具中的 400 个进程。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-gentlemen-raas-uses-gentlekiller-edr-framework-targeting-400-security-processes2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:09:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-gentlemen-raas-uses-gentlekiller-edr-framework-targeting-400-security-processes</guid></item></channel></rss>